      <method name="get_phase"
              c:identifier="foundry_build_pipeline_get_phase"
              glib:get-property="phase"
              version="1.1">
        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="libfoundry/build/foundry-build-pipeline.c"
             line="356">Gets the maximum phase reached by all completed stages.

The phase is calculated as the maximum phase of all stages that have
the completed property set to true, up to the first stage that is not
