              c:identifier="foundry_git_blame_dup_commit_id"
              version="1.1">
        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="libfoundry/git/foundry-git-blame.c"
             line="117">Gets the commit ID string for the given line number from the blame
information.

The commit ID is the hash of the commit that last modified the line.</doc>
