        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="libfoundry/git/foundry-git-commit-builder.c"
             line="299">The key identifier to use for signing the commit.

If set, the commit will be signed using the specified key and the
signing format. If not set, the commit will not be signed.</doc>
