      <property name="staged" transfer-ownership="none">
        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="libfoundry/git/foundry-git-commit-builder.c"
             line="358">A list model containing all files that are currently staged for commit.

The list model contains [class@Foundry.GitStatusEntry] objects representing
files in the working tree that have been staged. The list is updated
automatically as files are staged or unstaged.</doc>
        <type name="Gio.ListModel"/>
      </property>
      <property name="unstaged" transfer-ownership="none">
        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="libfoundry/git/foundry-git-commit-builder.c"
             line="373">A list model containing all files that have unstaged changes.

The list model contains [class@Foundry.GitStatusEntry] objects representing
files in the working tree that have been modified but not staged. The list
