      <method name="list_to_root" c:identifier="foundry_symbol_list_to_root">
        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="libfoundry/symbols/foundry-symbol.c"
             line="190">Asynchronously populates a [iface@Gio.ListModel] of [class@Foundry.Symbol]
starting from this symbol to the root symbol by following
[method@Foundry.Symbol.find_parent] until there are no more parents.

