        <doc xml:space="preserve"
             filename="libfoundry/editing/foundry-text-document.c"
             line="494">This function will resolve a new [class@Dex.Future] when the underlying
[iface@Foundry.TextBuffer] has changed.

Use this to invalidate external resources that rely on the contents of
the document buffer.

