      <doc xml:space="preserve"
           filename="libfoundry/editing/foundry-text-manager.c"
           line="37">Manages text documents and provides text editing services.

FoundryTextManager coordinates text buffer creation, document management, and
provides a unified interface for text editing operations. It handles document
loading, saving, and maintains relationships between files and their text representations.</doc>
